K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423a-1: a'arya sarba aa bha ya pra d'a na n'a ma dha ra ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423a-3: 'phags pa thams cad la mi 'jigs pa spyin pa zhes bya ba'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-0: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa @423b dus gcig na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-1: bcom ldan 'das yul ma ga dha nas yul rgyu zhing aa mra'i tshal du gshegs te byon nas aa mra'i tshal lus 'phags ri'i dbang po'i brag phug na bzhugs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-2: de nas lha'i dbang po brgya byin bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la mgo bos phyag 'tshal te phyogs gcig tu 'dug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-3: phyogs gcig tu 'dug nas lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-6: rab tu gnod par bgyid pa ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-9: bdag la yun ring por phyir rgol ba'i dgra lags na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-10: de las bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag la chos bstan du gsol /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-11: de skad ces gsol pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-12: bcom ldan 'das kyis lha'i dbang po brgya byin la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-14: khyod kyis thams cad la mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa'i rig sngags don thams cad byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-15: 'jigs pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-16: nad thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed pa; dug thams cad 'jil ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-17: mtshon thams cad rengs par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:423b-20: rkang bzhi pa thams cad rengs par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-23: ma mo'i gdon phung bar byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-25: zas su phreng ba za ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-26: zas su spos za ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-27: zas su me tog za ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-28: zas su bdug pa za ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-31: zas su mi gtsang ba za ba rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-32: zas su gcin 'thung ba rab tu phung bar byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-35: mkhris pa las gyur pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-36: bad kan las gyur pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-38: 'gro ba drag shul spyod pa rab tu 'jigs par byed pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-42: mtshang 'dru ba thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed pa 'di zungs shig dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424a-43: thams cad la mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa'i rig sngags bshad par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-0: aa de ma de pra ma @424b de; pra me di ri /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-11: k'a li pra k'a li tsanda /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-14: be ge aa ti be ge /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-31: bi ha na bi ha na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-32: sarba du shta pra dushtam n'a sha ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-33: sarba aa bha ya pra de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-34: bdag 'khro dang bcas pa 'jigs pa thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-36: nad 'go ba thams cad las srungs shig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-38: gnas 'dir bdag gi don thams cad 'grub par gyur cig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-42: sarba siddhi hi de ra te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-43: na ma: sarba buddha n'an sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-45: thams cad la mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa'i rig sngags tshig bzhi bcu rtsa gcig po 'di skud pa la mdud de bcings sam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-46: skra la mdud pa por ra ma; bzlas brjod byas sam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:424b-48: gi wang la lan gcig bsngags te bskus sam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-3: chus 'chi ba'i dus byed par mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-5: gsang sngags sbyor ba sgrub pa thams cad sbyor ba rnams kyis ma grub pa rnams grub par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-6: sbyar te grub pa rnams gzhan gyis mi tshugs par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-7: pha rol gyis bcings pa las grol bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-8: gzhan gyis rig sngags gcod par byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-9: bdag gi rig sngags 'phel bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-10: gdon thams cad phung bar byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-11: gdon gang gis mi gtong na yang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-12: de'i mgo aardza ka'i dog pa bzhin du tshal pa bdun du 'gas so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-13: de nas lha'i dbang po brgya byin de nyid du mi snang bar gyur to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas lha'i dbang po brgya byin yi rang ste bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-15: 'phags pa thams cad la mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa zhes bya ba'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-16: rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-18: zhu chen gyi lo tstsha ba bandhe ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-071:425a-19: skad gsar bcad kyis kyang bcos nas gtan la phab pa /
